title: Winter to summer in Siberia: then and now – in pictures
text:
Seasons in Siberia: winter to summer – in pictures These images of the Yenisei river in Siberia show the stark contrast different times of year bring to the same scene. Reuters photographer Ilya Naymushin recorded seven locations in winter and again in summer
Friday 4 September 2015 11.47 BST
Ilya Naymushin/Reuters
